{"tid":1135151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二千多年前，墨子已用「膠」來形容一個人的愚昧固執","createTime":"2019-05-02T06:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T08:13:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"760e78fc4594c93a1ef14a95fa7ad3d3000939a2","tid":1135151,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:40:25.000Z","msg":"而在二千多年前，墨子的《墨子》卷拾一《小取篇》已用「膠」來形容一個人的愚昧固執：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n小取第四拾五獲之親，人也。獲事其親，非事人也。其弟，美人也。愛弟，非愛美人也。車，木也。乘車，非乘木也。船，木也。乘船，非人木也。盜人，人也。多盜，非多人也。無盜，非無人也。奚以明之？惡多盜，非惡多人也。欲無盜，非欲無人也。世相與共是之。若若是，則雖盜人人也，愛盜非愛人也，不愛盜非不愛人也，殺盜人，非殺人也。無難盜無難矣。此與彼衕類，世有彼而不自非也，墨者有此而非之，無也故焉，所謂內「膠」外閉與心毋空乎，內「膠」而不解也，此乃是而不然者也。<br />\r\n且夫讀書，非好書也。且鬥雞，非雞也。好鬥雞，好雞也。且入井，非入井也。止且入井，止入井也。且出門，非出門也。止且出門，止出門也。若若是，且夭，非夭也。壽夭也，壽夭也。有命，非命也；非執有命，非命也。無難矣，此與彼衕類。世有彼而不自非也，墨者有此而罪非之，無也故焉，所謂內「膠」外閉與心毋空乎，內「膠」而不解也。此乃是而不然者也。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有網友提供資料指西方早於上世紀六拾年代亦已經將「硬膠」(Plastics)等衕愚蠢：<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOriginal Message -----<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFrom: &quot;ABC&quot; &lt;a@a.com&gt;<br />\r\nNewsgroups: 3talk.joke<br />\r\nSent: Tuesday, October 23, 2007 7:09 PM<br />\r\nSubject: 原來60年代已經有人用&quot;膠&quot;字黎話人<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&gt; 《畢業生》-- 摘自wiki百科<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt; 麥奎爾先生：我想跟你說一個字。就一個字。 (Mr. McGuire: I want to say one word to you. Just one word.)<br />\r\n&gt; 本&middot;布拉達剋：是什麼？(Benjamin: Yes, sir.)<br />\r\n&gt; 麥奎爾先生：你在聽嗎？(Mr. McGuire: Are you listening?)<br />\r\n&gt; 本&middot;布拉達剋：是的，我在聽。(Benjamin: Yes, I am.)<br />\r\n&gt; 麥奎爾先生：「膠！」。(Mr. McGuire: Plastics.)<br />\r\n&gt; 布拉達剋的父親：你不覺得這個主意有點愚蠢了？<br />\r\n&gt; 本&middot;布拉達剋：不！是愚蠢透頂了。"},{"pid":"b57e9dffdbcbaa4cfdbaa55d3dc9730abf4836ff","tid":1135151,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac788e20a9a73cab584959669665510e96e0893","tid":1135151,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e1b1cc0608f599c1d987903628e927d1e83517","tid":1135151,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35afb4276cf24ccbeeb2c76b3fb10c160f4bd1e6","tid":1135151,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"0868629a849f805b8b0ef5d2e7813ef3b4b3e818","tid":1135151,"uid":204272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"兩個膠唔同意思應該"},{"pid":"fc7c6eb5ed354fbf10d9e424b1bd0985a6664b6a","tid":1135151,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"墨子兼愛=大愛左膠"},{"pid":"accdf808301e5a57bb82f95a689664da917efba5","tid":1135151,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"哩個膠係咪&quot;膠著&quot;個膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n形容個人腦部膠著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a46858828a78d5a7f1e5601f9bb5bd57e47303","tid":1135151,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"accdf808301e5a57bb82f95a689664da917efba5","tid":1135151,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"哩個膠係咪&quot;膠著&quot;個膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n形容個人腦部膠著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"果個年代應該未有膠"},{"pid":"666c187cbba3262a6483dfc4c6a845b908656288","tid":1135151,"uid":45749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"墨攻真係好好睇<br />\n漫畫同電影都係"},{"pid":"748de6f6a3047d7b582b81f62fbd73a27c21e3c6","tid":1135151,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09a46858828a78d5a7f1e5601f9bb5bd57e47303"